subject: Swimming
Olympic Games (2012)
Olympic Games
Records and Achievements
lead_paragraph: Michael Phelps’s eight gold medals in 2008 did not sate his appetite. He still wants to lower his record in the 200-meter butterfly, which he again won at the Olympic trials.
